pageContext.claim: “So when I met [Melania], considered to be one of the most beautiful models in the world by everybody. One of the most beautiful, one of the most elegant and the thing I liked about her, she'd always go home at night everyone else was out partying all night....She was on covers before she became First Lady.”
pageContext.analysis: Melania Trump had some reasonable success as a model, but she was not among the top models of her era.
